## Overview

a Trading View Pine code that is for a BTC trading strategy 

Downtrend 15-minute time frame Short Scalp Trade:

Entry only on when the 21-Day SMA is under the 55-day SMA AND BBWP < 35%

Exist when PMARP <15% on a 15 min candle close OR 15 min candle closes above local range high OR current candle wicks above prior Trend High. 

## Usage Instructions

Pine Code Scrypt intended to be used in Trading View

